<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="29" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="10" pageNumber="29">Culture characteristics.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="10" pageNumber="29">Colonies hyaline at the beginning, becoming white to dark brown with age. Mycelium superficial on the 3% OA. Colony margin smooth. Colonies on 2% MEA flat, reaching 69 mm diam in 13 d at 30 °C. No growth observed at 5 °C. Optimal temperature for growth 25 °C.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
